Binibining Pilipinas 2004 bụ mbipụta nke iri anọ na otụ nke Binibining Pilipinas
O mere na Smart Araneta Coliseum na Quezon City, Metro Manila, Philippines na Machị 6, n'afọ 2004.
Na njedebe nke ihe omume ahụ, Carla Gay Balingit chiri Maricar Balagtas dị ka Binibining Pilipinas-Universe 2004
Maria Rafaela Yunon kpuchiri Maria Karla Bautista dị ka Bb
Pilipinas-World 2004, ebe Jhezarie Javier kpuchiri Margaret-Ann Bayot dị ka Bb
A kpọrọ Tracy Ann Javelona onye nke mbụ na eso onye meriri ya na Princess Jasmine Tiongson onye nke abụọ na esote onye meriri.
